Package: softmaxreg
Type: Package
Title: Training multilayer neural network for softmax regression and classification
Version: 1.1
Date: 2016-07-07
Author: Xichen Ding <rockingdingo@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Xichen Ding <rockingdingo@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 2.10), methods
Description: This package implements softmax regression and classfication models with multilayer neural network. It can be used for many tasks like word embedding based document classification, MNIST handwritten digit recognition and so on. Multiple optimization algorithm including SGD, Adagrad, RMSprop, Momentum, NAG, etc are also provided.
License: GPL (>= 2)
